      <h2>Format</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>10 rounds × 10 questions (100 total).</li>
        <li>30 seconds per question.</li>
        <li>Mostly typed answers, with one multiple-choice round.</li>
        <li>Answers are <strong>case-insensitive</strong> and must match exactly.</li>
        <li>Points are awarded for <strong>speed + accuracy</strong>.</li>
        <li>Leaderboard is shown <strong>between rounds</strong> only.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Rules</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>One device per ticket</strong> (one ticket = one player).</li>
        <li>No spelling variants — I’ve picked unambiguous answers.</li>
        <li>Keep it fun. Don’t be a maniac.</li>
        <li>Host decisions are final (even if you’re fuming).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How you’ll join</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You’ll watch via a YouTube livestream link.</li>
        <li>We’ll send the livestream link <strong>1 hour before</strong> kickoff.</li>
      </ul>
